These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea
City: new-york, miami
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, balloon-flower
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, bus
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, baccarat
There are 2 different favourite colors: amber, blood-red
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, april
1. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami##3
2. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
4. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
6. the person driving the bus is the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | tea        | hot-chocolate |
| City          | miami  | new-york     |
| Flower         | balloon-flower    | bellflower         |
| Transport           | car    | bus |
| Cigar   | bongani  | baccarat     |
| Color           | blood-red      | amber    |
| Birthday         | april | march          |

