.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, swisher
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, february
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, western
2 different games are played: monopoly, domino
House: farmhouse, victorian
There are 2 different favourite colors: lilac, chestnut
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, corn
1. the victorian house is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
2. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person eating corn is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |
| Cigar         | old-henry      | swisher       |
| Birthday           | march | february |
| Movie-Genre   | western      | horror        |
| Game   | monopoly         | domino        |
| House   | farmhouse    | victorian       |
| Color           | chestnut        | lilac          |
| Food     | corn          | pomegranate    |

