2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |
| Birthday      | march | december  |
| House          | victorian   | gothic-revival   |
